Helix::Driver::DB::MySQL, version 0.01
======================================

The Helix::Driver::DB::MySQL is the MySQL database driver for Helix Framework.
MySQL versions 4.0+ are supported. 

INSTALLATION

To install the driver type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

To use this driver you must have the following packages installed:

    DBI
    DBD::mysql
    Helix

